message.body: Hey love :) do you have Saturday (tomorrow) plans? I'll be hanging out with Scott for most of the day!

Martha! I'm sorry I didn't respond to your email yet. I have been trying to figure out my schedule before I told you something that would change. I have grad school group work tomorrow morning, then have to do some wedding stuff for two friends' weddings, and need to be in Faribault by early evening. :( I don't have specific times but will let you know if there are gaps tomorrow!! When do you leave?
